<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 5:55
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='344687' id='t-344687'>Obviously the Church weren't very happy about this,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='347123' id='t-347123'>and they tried to suppress it,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='349224' id='t-349224'>but what they hadn't counted on was technology,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='352295' id='t-352295'>and then they had the printing press, which suddenly</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='354720' id='t-354720'>enabled these ideas to spread cheaply, far and fast,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='358112' id='t-358112'>and people would come together in coffee houses,</span>
