<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='409283' id='t-409283'>of information, and analyze it to make good decisions.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:04
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='413049' id='t-413049'>So that's why we're seeing increasingly this demand</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='416075' id='t-416075'>for access to information.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='418460' id='t-418460'>That's why we're starting to see more disclosure laws</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='420769' id='t-420769'>come out, so for example, on the environment,</span>
