<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='460211' id='t-460211'>And they're all moving to this central system,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='463003' id='t-463003'>this fully connected system,</span>
