<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='579014' id='t-579014'>This is Birgitta Jónsdóttir. She's an Icelandic MP.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='583309' id='t-583309'>And quite an unusual MP. In Iceland, she was</span>
