12:07
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='716777' id='t-716777'>Another rather large investigation is around world diplomacy.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='722345' id='t-722345'>Again, this is all based around leaks,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='724845' id='t-724845'>251,000 U.S. diplomatic cables, and I was involved</span>
